parameters.name: catalog_name
parameters.description: The identifier of the catalog under which to list registered models.             If specified, schema_name must be specified.

parameters.name: schema_name
parameters.description: The identifier of the schema under which to list registered models.             If specified, catalog_name must be specified.

parameters.name: max_results
parameters.description: Max number of registered models to return.

parameters.name: page_token
parameters.description: Opaque token to send for the next page of results (pagination).

parameters.name: include_browse
parameters.description: Whether to include registered models in the response for which the principal can only access selective metadata for

200.description: The registered model list was successfully retrieved

401.description: The request does not have valid authentication credentials for the operation.

403.description: Caller does not have permission to execute the specified operation.

404.description: Operation was performed on a resource that does not exist.

get.description: List registered models. You can list registered models under a particular schema, or list all registered models in the current metastore.
